OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:
OL,6,
OL,7,CTonight:FClear intervals and blustery
OL,8,Fshowers this evening the fresh to
OL,9,Fstrong westerly winds then easing
OL,10,Ftonight with the showers becoming more
OL,11,Fisolated.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA few light showers in the
OL,14,Fmorning otherwise a dry bright day
OL,15,Fwith some sunny spells, lighter winds.
OL,16,FHigh cloud thickening later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
